title: Account Transfer
body:
How long does it take to transfer from EUNE to NA have been waiting for almost a day now...Still says: Your account is in the process of transferring. Please try again in a few minutes.

I've been waiting for almost a day now. When will the suffering stop rito?

replies.body: It can vary, sometimes it's intent but it could also take a bit.  It's also patch day, so all the regions need to be sync'd up on the same patch to continue as well.   I looked into your specific case, and it doesn't look like the transfer processed (likely due to the patch).  You may need to try again!  Let me know if that clears things up!
Things have cleared up! But will my name now permanently be: tempkhklihykffdp?
Since you were on NA before, it looks like your name became inactive but the flag didn't follow through.  I've flagged your account for a rename, so it should be good to go now!
